                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable F</hi> 98.) I was called in—I saw the boxes lying open on the bed—the prisoner was standing near them—she turned out</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184301300096"></xptr>
               <p>some of the things until Mr. Thompson saw this watch guard—he laid hold of that—some bracelets were found in the bottom of the box—she acknow<lb></lb>ledged they were Mr. Thompson's property—we got them all out on the table—she said, "As for the coats and trowsers, Master Charles, I know nothing about them, but I acknowledge to these things here"—pointing to these articles.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
